# 🗳️ E-Voting System

An online E-Voting System built using modern web technologies to ensure secure, transparent, and accessible elections. This system supports voter authentication, admin access, and real-time vote casting with a responsive and modern UI.

🌐 **Live Demo**: [luxury-crepe-25e2f0.netlify.app](https://luxury-crepe-25e2f0.netlify.app/)

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 Voter and Admin Authentication
- ✅ Secure Vote Casting (one vote per user)
- 📊 Real-time Voting Results (Admin only)
- 📁 Supabase Backend Integration
- ⚙️ Admin Panel to Manage Elections
- 🧑‍💼 Voter Registration System
- 🔄 Fully Responsive Design

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React + TypeScript
- **State Management**: Zustand
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Icons/UI**: Lucide, TailwindCSS, Custom UI Components
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth)
- **Deployment**: Netlify

